If you do make a mistake, be like Billy Burke and be quick to repent.

00:49:27.209 --> 00:49:41.966
He talked about how a water moccasin came into his house because he left the patio door open.

00:49:41.966 --> 00:49:49.102
It was his fault for letting the snake in.

00:49:59.474 --> 00:50:00.857
We aren't afraid of bird flu; we have the honey glow.

00:50:00.857 --> 00:50:17.347
The anointing of the Holy Spirit was like a honey glow that the virus couldn't penetrate.

00:50:17.347 --> 00:50:32.966
As we walked into those tents, we laid hands on people and they were healed.

00:50:39.446 --> 00:50:44.799
I thank You, Lord, that their hands will prosper in 2025.

00:50:46.068 --> 00:50:48.685
They will be the head and not the tail.

00:50:55.280 --> 00:51:00.111
We will show the world there is a living Jesus inside of us.

00:51:00.111 --> 00:51:09.173
Subscribe to our videos and click the notification bell.

00:51:09.173 --> 00:51:16.290
Braden helped me with the tech.

00:51:18.020 --> 00:51:22.084
Pray for the people of North Korea.

00:51:22.084 --> 00:51:26.000
Father, we lift them up.

00:51:26.000 --> 00:51:37.084
May they find Jesus before it's too late.

00:51:48.667 --> 00:51:49.040
We pray for peace over Ukraine and Russia.

00:51:49.040 --> 00:51:53.520
May this needless war cease.

00:51:53.520 --> 00:52:04.435
Father, may Donald Trump be a voice in the darkness.

00:52:09.640 --> 00:52:22.405
I ask You, Father, that we would spare this generation from this virus, just as Abraham petitioned You for Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:52:22.405 --> 00:52:29.060
We give You all the glory.

00:52:29.060 --> 00:52:31.439
Amen.
